Rick is a self-proclaimed King Kotini. Meaning king of cotton, it's a term he coined to describe someone who is well dressed."I'm aware that I'm being watched internationally and continentally because of my style, and fashion is something I've always been interested in," he says.READ MORE: The secret's out: Maps Maponyane &amp; Riky Rick share their grooming routines"I pay attention to small details like the shape of collar and length of pants. I also keep up to date with international fashion trends. I'm not a typical rapper wearing only sneakers."Everything he wears he has bought himself. "I'm unapologetic about my style and I have an interest in fashion even if it's expensive". This article is adapted from one originally published in the Sunday Times. Read the original article.